From cf5aaae2261a97deb2dcd3093157bda6be5b3a19 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Vivek Chettri <vchettri@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 28 Jul 2025 19:40:14 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM: CP: wifi: ath12k: Add support for to display SCS
 information.

Add support to display the SCS information for a STA for which
SCS sessions are active.

The following SCS related inforamtion would be printed per STA
	SCS ID
	SCS Request Type (R2/R3, DownLink/UpLink)
	QoS Profile ID
	MSDUQ/TID Information
	QoS parameters (for R3 SCS)

Following is the sample for few SCS request on a client

root@OpenWrt:~# cat
